# Initialise Git
$ Git init

# 

















# All about branches

# Create a new branch
$ git branch kojo

# Switch to an existing branch
$ git checkout kojo

# Create a new branch and Switch to it
$ git checkout -b quame

# Delete a branch
$ git branch -d quame

# List all branches
$ git branch

##
The head is a pointer to your last commit. It moves with you when you switch branches.




# Git status
$ git status

